reviewText: This is one of the best Girls Gone Wild that I've bought.  It is shorter, only 43 minutes long.  But from 21 to 26 minutes on the counter is a good 5 minute solo, spread, 1 finger and 2 finger.  Near the end, another girl shows off her new piercing, see everything.  And there is the usual flashing in clubs, booby bouncing, girl-girl, etc.
This is one of their good series with the exception of Vol 2 which is mostly a rerun of vol 1 but not as good. If your going to buy go with #1-3&4. Good girl/girl and solos.
